1
00:00:00,950 --> 00:00:04,010
The Cage of Love

2
00:00:04,010 --> 00:00:07,110
<i> Episode 2 </i>

3
00:00:16,020 --> 00:00:18,070
Boss. You are looking for me?

4
00:00:18,070 --> 00:00:21,350
Ling Long is in trouble.

5
00:00:21,350 --> 00:00:26,400
There's a dye factory called Yao Sheng, selling their products at a lower price, to drive Ling Long out of business.

6
00:00:26,400 --> 00:00:30,060
How can this be?
Our Ling Long is a well-known brand,

7
00:00:30,060 --> 00:00:32,770
with many customers and quality goods.

8
00:00:32,770 --> 00:00:35,930
Yao Sheng used dyes imported from France.

9
00:00:35,930 --> 00:00:41,170
The textiles they produce are okay,
but their price is 10 percent cheaper than ours.

10
00:00:41,170 --> 00:00:43,730
However, the cost of importing dyes is expensive.

11
00:00:43,730 --> 00:00:46,390
How could their textiles be cheaper than ours?

12
00:00:46,390 --> 00:00:49,530
I think that Yao Sheng is disregarding costs,

13
00:00:49,530 --> 00:00:52,180
and doing cut-throat competition.

14
00:00:52,180 --> 00:00:58,200
Have someone look up Yao Sheng's backing.
Also, take a look and see how much money we have left in our account.

15
00:00:58,200 --> 00:01:01,920
We must defeat them this time.

16
00:01:03,290 --> 00:01:05,160
Yes.

17
00:01:21,740 --> 00:01:23,900
Shao Tian.

18
00:01:26,830 --> 00:01:29,940
What's wrong? Why do you look hassled?

19
00:01:31,120 --> 00:01:34,610
Shao Tian. Listen to me. I just transferred the money out.

20
00:01:34,610 --> 00:01:37,790
Wu Hong Da suddenly wants to check the balance of the accounts.

21
00:01:37,790 --> 00:01:40,630
He says it's to deal with the cut-throat competition.

22
00:01:40,630 --> 00:01:43,940
Tell me what we should do.

23
00:01:46,010 --> 00:01:50,280
It was such a big sum of money and you dared to steal it.
It's causing a stir now.

24
00:01:50,280 --> 00:01:51,960
You're so scared that you're about to piss.

25
00:01:51,960 --> 00:01:55,480
If they investigate the huge sum of money, we will be in trouble.

26
00:01:55,480 --> 00:01:59,690
You don't know Wu Hong Da. He is very cruel.

27
00:01:59,690 --> 00:02:03,190
Of course, I know what kind of person he is.

28
00:02:03,190 --> 00:02:06,610
I schemed about this money for a long time.

29
00:02:06,610 --> 00:02:08,620
Don't worry.

30
00:02:08,620 --> 00:02:13,610
I'm his eyes. You are his hands.

31
00:02:13,610 --> 00:02:18,290
We know very well what actions he will take.

32
00:02:18,290 --> 00:02:21,700
Shao Tian. Didn't you say that we would leave Huzhou once the money was in our hands?

33
00:02:21,700 --> 00:02:24,040
When will we leave?

34
00:02:25,290 --> 00:02:27,000
Very soon.

35
00:02:27,000 --> 00:02:31,040
I have a plan. Don't be impulsive.

36
00:02:32,590 --> 00:02:37,020
Shao Tian. The money will be in our hands soon.
Why aren't we leaving?

37
00:02:37,790 --> 00:02:41,900
It can't be that you really like the Miss of the Wu family?

38
00:02:41,900 --> 00:02:44,390
You want to be their son-in-law?

39
00:02:44,390 --> 00:02:46,930
I'm saying, Shao Tian. Stop dreaming.

40
00:02:46,930 --> 00:02:52,770
If Miss knew you are scheming with her father behind her back,
she would chew and spit you out in a second.

41
00:03:01,570 --> 00:03:04,260
Don't get involved in my affairs.

42
00:03:04,260 --> 00:03:06,370
I know what to do.

43
00:03:11,810 --> 00:03:13,870
Have you seen this person?

44
00:03:13,870 --> 00:03:16,140
No.

45
00:03:16,140 --> 00:03:18,570
Hello. Have you seen this person?

46
00:03:18,570 --> 00:03:21,420
Okay, you can leave first.

47
00:03:21,420 --> 00:03:23,710
Manager Jiang.

48
00:03:27,730 --> 00:03:31,480
Madam Jiang's illness is not stable. It's worse than before.

49
00:03:31,480 --> 00:03:34,390
And there wasn't any symptoms before her illness started.

50
00:03:34,390 --> 00:03:37,510
We, the medical staff, have been trying our best to help her,

51
00:03:37,510 --> 00:03:40,240
but have had little success.

52
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:44,870
When she is discharged, you and Miss Fang must work hard to persuade her.

53
00:03:44,870 --> 00:03:48,970
Perhaps, she might accept the advice of her family members.

54
00:03:50,500 --> 00:03:53,990
It has been many years. When my mom thinks of unhappy events,

55
00:03:53,990 --> 00:03:56,560
she becomes like this.

56
00:03:56,560 --> 00:04:00,430
We have tried many methods and consulted many doctors

57
00:04:00,430 --> 00:04:03,270
but there is no progress.

58
00:04:05,470 --> 00:04:08,410
Mom. What are you doing?

59
00:04:08,410 --> 00:04:09,690
Give me the scissors.

60
00:04:09,690 --> 00:04:13,920
Yu Er. I don't want to live anymore.

61
00:04:13,920 --> 00:04:17,170
If I die, you don't have to suffer so much.

62
00:04:17,170 --> 00:04:21,840
Madam Jiang. Let's talk it over. Your son is here.

63
00:04:21,840 --> 00:04:25,240
- Don't do anything foolish.
- It's useless.

64
00:04:25,240 --> 00:04:28,060
They forced my husband to die.

65
00:04:28,060 --> 00:04:31,550
They are thinking of forcing me and the Wu family.

66
00:04:31,550 --> 00:04:33,710
- Mom.
- Don't move.

67
00:04:33,710 --> 00:04:37,020
Okay, I won't move. Don't do anything either.

68
00:04:37,020 --> 00:04:39,160
Don't move.

69
00:04:39,160 --> 00:04:43,380
You have suffered for the past few years.

70
00:04:43,380 --> 00:04:48,000
I didn't take good care care of you. Instead, you had to take care of me instead.

71
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:54,360
When I'm dead, you don't have use your savings to treat me.

72
00:04:54,950 --> 00:04:57,730
I really can't drag you down any longer.

73
00:04:57,730 --> 00:05:00,050
Mom, don't say this. You are not dragging me down.

74
00:05:00,050 --> 00:05:02,360
When I die,

75
00:05:02,360 --> 00:05:05,410
I can be free. You can be free too.

76
00:05:05,410 --> 00:05:07,460
Aunt.

77
00:05:11,290 --> 00:05:13,370
Mom.

78
00:05:13,370 --> 00:05:16,960
Doctor, help me to treat her wound.

79
00:05:17,640 --> 00:05:21,580
Aunt. You said that you wanted to be free and didn't want to drag anyone down.

80
00:05:21,580 --> 00:05:26,620
Actually, you are trying to run away and using the pain as your excuse.

81
00:05:28,520 --> 00:05:32,810
Do you think that if you die, they will really be relieved?

82
00:05:32,810 --> 00:05:34,690
You are wrong.

83
00:05:34,690 --> 00:05:36,860
Your death will only bring them more pain.

84
00:05:36,860 --> 00:05:40,200
They will only hate themselves for not being able to protect their own mother.

85
00:05:40,200 --> 00:05:44,600
They will also be in pain as to why you wouldn't shoulder this with them.

86
00:05:44,600 --> 00:05:47,060
You are also leaving all your pain to them.

87
00:05:47,060 --> 00:05:51,970
They will never be able to forgive you and themselves.

88
00:05:52,810 --> 00:05:58,040
Four years ago, my mom and I were in the same situation as you.

89
00:05:58,040 --> 00:06:03,650
To relieve me, she chose to kill herself.

90
00:06:03,650 --> 00:06:09,620
These years, I've been living in a painful abyss.

91
00:06:10,250 --> 00:06:12,630
If you want your son to be like me,

92
00:06:12,630 --> 00:06:15,970
everyday living while blaming oneself, then do it!

93
00:06:17,700 --> 00:06:21,710
Remember, next time find someplace where there'll be no one around.

94
00:06:21,710 --> 00:06:24,500
No one will disturb you again.

95
00:06:27,990 --> 00:06:31,740
Everything should be alright. Take a rest soon.

96
00:06:42,670 --> 00:06:44,520
Nurse. Where is the outpatient clinic?

97
00:06:44,520 --> 00:06:46,150
Over there.

98
00:06:46,150 --> 00:06:48,040
Thanks.

99
00:06:58,000 --> 00:07:09,910
