100
00:07:19,890 --> 00:07:21,670
Sorry about just now.

101
00:07:21,670 --> 00:07:25,640
Your apology doesn't sound sincere.

102
00:07:27,510 --> 00:07:31,870
I never thought you also had experienced
the same hardships I did.

103
00:07:33,390 --> 00:07:35,930
My mom was just like your mom.

104
00:07:35,930 --> 00:07:40,890
For many years, she had to endure the pain caused by her illness.

105
00:07:40,890 --> 00:07:46,300
The many years of suffering caused her to turn from gentle to bad-tempered.

106
00:07:46,300 --> 00:07:49,030
Her love for me also

107
00:07:49,030 --> 00:07:52,830
made her decide to free herself for my sake.

108
00:07:53,700 --> 00:07:58,920
When she made her decision, she didn't consider my feelings.

109
00:08:00,100 --> 00:08:02,990
Up until my mom left me,

110
00:08:02,990 --> 00:08:05,650
it was too late to feel regretful.

111
00:08:06,710 --> 00:08:10,610
If before she made this absurd decision,

112
00:08:10,610 --> 00:08:13,900
I could have told her what was in my heart,

113
00:08:13,900 --> 00:08:16,990
she wouldn't have done that.

114
00:08:23,520 --> 00:08:26,940
Twelve years ago, our family suffered a catastrophe.

115
00:08:28,210 --> 00:08:31,960
From then on, my mom developed a mental illness.

116
00:08:32,940 --> 00:08:36,310
For these twelve years, we've always been cautious.

117
00:08:36,310 --> 00:08:40,560
Not knowing which word or which situation would provoke her.

118
00:08:41,580 --> 00:08:46,050
But the more we didn't dare say,
the tighter the knot in my mom's heart got.

119
00:08:47,300 --> 00:08:51,560
Her illness became more serious.

120
00:08:51,560 --> 00:08:56,260
I didn't expect that you causing a scene, would instead undo the knot in her heart.

121
00:08:57,370 --> 00:09:00,320
Since I did you such a big favour,

122
00:09:00,320 --> 00:09:02,910
shouldn't you declare something to me?

123
00:09:02,910 --> 00:09:04,690
Declare what?

124
00:09:04,690 --> 00:09:06,920
That fountain pen.

125
00:09:09,220 --> 00:09:12,600
How could be you so stubborn?

126
00:09:12,600 --> 00:09:16,890
Yes, you did help me but you also hurt my mom.

127
00:09:16,890 --> 00:09:19,550
Hence, we are considered even. We don't owe each other anything.

128
00:09:19,550 --> 00:09:23,750
In that situation just now, if I didn't do that, would she have came to her senses?

129
00:09:23,750 --> 00:09:26,310
Rotten Stone Head. I did you such a big favour

130
00:09:26,310 --> 00:09:28,580
and you are still unwilling to let me have the pen?

131
00:09:28,580 --> 00:09:31,000
Aren't you being a little stingy?

132
00:09:33,550 --> 00:09:38,600
If you find out my name, I will then reconsider if I should give it to you.

133
00:09:38,600 --> 00:09:40,670
- Rotten Stone Head.
- And also,

134
00:09:40,670 --> 00:09:43,360
don't hassle the doctors and the nurses.

135
00:09:43,360 --> 00:09:46,500
I already told them to protect the information of the patient.

136
00:09:46,500 --> 00:09:48,850
If not, I will sue them.

137
00:09:48,850 --> 00:09:52,750
I don't need to ask them. I already know your rotten name.

138
00:09:56,300 --> 00:09:58,850
It's Rotten Stone Head.

139
00:10:10,710 --> 00:10:12,960
Brother Shao Tian, why are you here?

140
00:10:12,960 --> 00:10:15,670
I went to your house to look for you. They told me that you were at the hospital.

141
00:10:15,670 --> 00:10:19,580
I witnessed your heroic deed in saving someone.

142
00:10:19,580 --> 00:10:23,390
Our little heroine is injured. Let me bandage your wound.

143
00:10:23,390 --> 00:10:25,970
It's already done.

144
00:10:26,950 --> 00:10:29,550
That fast?

145
00:10:31,010 --> 00:10:34,510
-Who was that man?
-Are you referring to Rotten Stone Head?

146
00:10:34,510 --> 00:10:37,490
He is the guy who snatched my pen.

147
00:10:52,920 --> 00:10:56,940
Cai Hong, I like you.

148
00:10:56,940 --> 00:11:00,620
I want to take you for my wife.

149
00:11:09,380 --> 00:11:12,930
Cai Hong. You don't need to answer me right now.

150
00:11:12,930 --> 00:11:14,620
You really don't need to.

151
00:11:14,620 --> 00:11:16,620
You just need to know that in this world,

152
00:11:16,620 --> 00:11:19,690
there is always someone waiting for you by your side.

153
00:11:19,690 --> 00:11:23,990
No matter when or where, no matter the circumstances,

154
00:11:23,990 --> 00:11:27,420
I will always be waiting for you.

155
00:11:38,840 --> 00:11:41,020
Brother.

156
00:11:45,770 --> 00:11:49,310
Here's today's newspaper. It has news about Ling Long.

157
00:12:01,600 --> 00:12:04,130
Petty devil. Petty devil.

158
00:12:04,130 --> 00:12:06,330
You're really narrow-minded.

159
00:12:06,330 --> 00:12:08,610
I saved your mom

160
00:12:08,610 --> 00:12:11,760
and you still won't let me have the pen.

161
00:12:11,760 --> 00:12:15,900
I should visit his mom but I hit her yesterday.

162
00:12:15,900 --> 00:12:18,980
Would she remember and hate me?

163
00:12:18,980 --> 00:12:25,050
No. In order to give my Dad a surprise, I must find out his name.

164
00:12:27,670 --> 00:12:30,850
Wu Long.

165
00:12:30,850 --> 00:12:35,910
Kitty, I don't have time to play with you today.
I have a very important task to do.

166
00:12:35,910 --> 00:12:39,970
See you later. Keep the rabbit company.

167
00:12:51,280 --> 00:12:53,280
Who is it?

168
00:12:53,280 --> 00:12:55,430
Come in.

169
00:12:56,150 --> 00:12:58,010
Aunt.

170
00:12:58,010 --> 00:12:59,490
It's you.

171
00:12:59,490 --> 00:13:02,570
-Don't get up.
-Come here.

172
00:13:03,850 --> 00:13:06,700
Lie down. Don't get up.

173
00:13:06,700 --> 00:13:09,090
Come and sit.

174
00:13:10,510 --> 00:13:13,800
Aunt, sorry about yesterday.

175
00:13:13,800 --> 00:13:16,910
I'm here to apologise to you today.

176
00:13:16,910 --> 00:13:20,100
You really don't need to apologise to me.

177
00:13:20,100 --> 00:13:25,110
Yesterday, fortunately, you slapped me and made me come to my senses.

178
00:13:25,110 --> 00:13:29,710
Otherwise I would still be bashing my head against a brick wall.

179
00:13:29,710 --> 00:13:34,950
Actually, I have been hurting my family all these years.

180
00:13:38,370 --> 00:13:41,410
Once I'm discharged, I will treat you to a meal.

181
00:13:41,410 --> 00:13:46,750
I don't need the meal but if you really want to thank me,

182
00:13:46,750 --> 00:13:49,970
you can tell me your son's name.

183
00:13:51,740 --> 00:13:54,430
If you have any matters with him, you can wait for him to come later.

184
00:13:54,430 --> 00:13:57,670
Why don't you ask him yourself?

185
00:14:03,340 --> 00:14:06,960
He won't tell me when he sees me.

186
00:14:06,960 --> 00:14:09,330
Why?

187
00:14:09,960 --> 00:14:12,940
It's a long story.

188
00:14:13,730 --> 00:14:16,010
Hello, Mr Jiang.

189
00:14:18,870 --> 00:14:20,710
Mom.

190
00:14:21,510 --> 00:14:23,360
Mom.

191
00:14:27,450 --> 00:14:29,510
You are here.

192
00:14:29,510 --> 00:14:30,790
Mom, what are you doing?

193
00:14:30,790 --> 00:14:34,980
I'm tired of lying down and wanted to move around.

194
00:14:44,970 --> 00:14:47,670
Yu... Jiang Yu.

195
00:14:47,670 --> 00:14:51,580
Is your work done at the factory?

196
00:14:52,530 --> 00:14:58,580
Jiang Yu. If you are busy, you don't need to visit me.

197
00:15:00,170 --> 00:15:02,620
I'm fine.

198
00:15:04,780 --> 00:15:09,740
Son, don't worry. I'm really fine.

199
00:15:09,740 --> 00:15:12,040
Mom, are you really okay?

200
00:15:24,880 --> 00:15:27,030
What are you doing?

201
00:15:27,940 --> 00:15:30,500
Mom. What is she doing here?

202
00:15:34,020 --> 00:15:35,850
What are you both doing?

203
00:15:35,850 --> 00:15:37,630
We didn't do anything.

204
00:15:37,630 --> 00:15:41,410
I only promised her that I would call your name.

205
00:15:41,410 --> 00:15:45,970
I already know your name.
It's Jiang Yu.

206
00:15:47,890 --> 00:15:49,980
Let's go.

207
00:15:49,980 --> 00:15:51,520
Let's go.

208
00:15:51,520 --> 00:15:56,000
I only just called his name. What's wrong?

209
00:15:59,050 --> 00:16:00,970
Take this.

210
00:16:02,610 --> 00:16:04,640
Where is my fountain pen?

211
00:16:04,640 --> 00:16:07,430
Don't you remember what I said the other time?

212
00:16:07,430 --> 00:16:11,240
I said that once you found out my name, we would discuss this again.

213
00:16:11,240 --> 00:16:15,350
I didn't promise that I would give you the pen immediately.

214
00:16:16,050 --> 00:16:20,900
Rotten Stone Head. A kid knows what a promise is.

215
00:16:20,900 --> 00:16:24,470
You are going to be a scoundrel over a pen?

216
00:16:24,470 --> 00:16:26,170
Even I feel ashamed for you.

217
00:16:26,170 --> 00:16:28,660
Okay. Even if I promised to give you the fountain pen,

218
00:16:28,660 --> 00:16:32,270
it was agreed on that you couldn't spend any money.

219
00:16:32,270 --> 00:16:36,090
You bribed my mom. You broke the pact first.

220
00:16:36,090 --> 00:16:38,630
When did I bribe your mom?

221
00:16:38,630 --> 00:16:42,480
Did you make this appear from thin air?

222
00:16:42,480 --> 00:16:46,290
This is to declare my sincerity. That's why I bought this for her.

223
00:16:46,290 --> 00:16:48,040
I didn't have any intentions to bribe her at all.

224
00:16:48,040 --> 00:16:51,950
In any case, I have only two words. Definitely not.

225
00:16:51,950 --> 00:16:55,520
Then I also have two words. Shame-less.

226
00:16:57,880 --> 00:17:01,730
Okay. Seeing how pitiful and miserable you are,

227
00:17:01,730 --> 00:17:06,390
I will give you another chance. Don't spend a single cent or go through my mom,

228
00:17:06,390 --> 00:17:08,980
just find out my favourite food.

229
00:17:08,980 --> 00:17:12,790
I will consider whether to let you have the pen then.

230
00:17:14,960 --> 00:17:17,520
Jiang Yu. You don't keep your promise.

231
00:17:17,520 --> 00:17:20,970
I don't believe that I can't find the exact same pen.

232
00:17:20,970 --> 00:17:25,220
Miss. There was really only one of that pen. I'm not lying to you.

233
00:17:25,220 --> 00:17:28,510
There is only one in Huzhou. It can't be that there is also only one in this world.

234
00:17:28,510 --> 00:17:31,370
Miss. If you really like that fountain pen,

235
00:17:31,370 --> 00:17:34,550
I can send a telegraph to the overseas manufacturer to order another one,

236
00:17:34,550 --> 00:17:37,600
but it will take a long time. It takes around twenty days.

237
00:17:37,600 --> 00:17:41,950
Twenty days? My father's birthday celebration is in ten days. It will be too late for me.

238
00:17:41,950 --> 00:17:44,270
Why don't you look around my shop for another gift?

239
00:17:44,270 --> 00:17:47,980
I don't want to. I only want that fountain pen.

240
00:17:58,380 --> 00:18:01,380
<i>I will treat you to a meal another day. What do you like to eat?</i>

241
00:18:01,380 --> 00:18:03,500
<i>I can treat you to anything.</i>

242
00:18:03,500 --> 00:18:05,090
Stop the rickshaw.

243
00:18:09,480 --> 00:18:13,350
It's really you.

244
00:18:13,350 --> 00:18:17,180
Come. What are you doing here?

245
00:18:17,180 --> 00:18:19,980
Where is your fierce owner?

246
00:18:21,970 --> 00:18:25,890
Did you leave home? Are you afraid of her too?

247
00:18:25,890 --> 00:18:30,980
Why don't we do this? I will take you to visit my home.

248
00:18:30,980 --> 00:18:33,590
Okay, let's go.

249
00:18:36,940 --> 00:18:39,720
Brother. What are you doing?

250
00:18:39,720 --> 00:18:43,280
A cat is here. So cute.

251
00:18:43,280 --> 00:18:45,990
-I picked it up.
